{"word":"G5521 - χολή - cholḗ - khol-ay' - Gall","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χολή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">cholḗ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khol-ay'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Gall</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"கசப்பு - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"bile, gall"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Feminine of an equivalent perhaps akin to the same as <a href=\"#/G5514 - Χλόη - Chlóē - khlo'-ay/5514\">G5514</a> (from the <i>greenish</i> hue); &ldquo;gall&rdquo; or <i>bile</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>poison</i> or an <i>anodyne</i> (wormwood, poppy, etc.): - gall.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}